{"tid":1775403,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"發現咗老豆有個細30年二奶半個月，患病母親今日堅決攤派","createTime":"2019-12-08T23:55:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-10T00:51:14.000Z","uid":269707,"like":13,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"508d30b44426c86f782580f29f0c8563deff5f74","tid":1775403,"uid":269707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-08T23:55:52.000Z","msg":"是咁的，早半個月我同呀媽留意到佢晚晚成十二點先返，之後又留意到佢同個女人晚晚WTSAPP，早幾日又發現佢手機好多同個女人一齊嘅相。宜家怕個女人係貪佢退休金，樓又冇呀媽名，佢晚晚若無其事，呀媽有高血壓，唔受得咁大打擊<br />\n到琴晚，二奶話今晚要同老豆去爆房。今朝，我有長期病患嘅呀媽決定同細過我幾年嘅二奶攤派，我唔知會有咩後果，不過係我都忍唔到，呢件事比三年前在TVB落選港男慘千百倍，我可能就在今晚回到家失去媽媽和家庭。好不容易才搵到份高收入嘅工作，屋企黑警老豆點解又搞咁嘅事出嚟"},{"pid":"89798310e2f7d1f7e22aea6ee80499220b4fb59c","tid":1775403,"uid":72457,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-08T23:59:55.000Z","msg":"因為二奶撑警"},{"pid":"b631d219e7d136fce4e32125456c125d62dd44d1","tid":1775403,"uid":51936,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T00:02:09.000Z","msg":"潮文？<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"73e23ea0e4c2aac1951c3704b213b93447d1cabf","tid":1775403,"uid":269707,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"89798310e2f7d1f7e22aea6ee80499220b4fb59c","tid":1775403,"uid":72457,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-08T23:59:55.000Z","msg":"因為二奶撑警"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T00:04:28.000Z","msg":"老豆係克驚"},{"pid":"d1084eddea8f804e9efe12d735b3216c449b6386","tid":1775403,"uid":269707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b631d219e7d136fce4e32125456c125d62dd44d1","tid":1775403,"uid":51936,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T00:02:09.000Z","msg":"潮文？<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T00:05:29.000Z","msg":"潮汝老板，關乎我老母嘅命"},{"pid":"585be96a306949636cc532bc931bc2e8319e7242","tid":1775403,"uid":261849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T00:05:50.000Z","msg":"你去媾左個二奶啦<img src=\"/a